"the three is contact."

msgctxt "mn148:7.9"
msgid "‘Cha phassakāyā veditabbā’ti—"
msgstr "‘The six classes of contact should be understood.’"

msgctxt "mn148:7.10"
msgid "iti yaṃ taṃ vuttaṃ, idametaṃ paṭicca vuttaṃ."
msgstr "That’s what I said, and this is why I said it."

msgctxt "mn148:7.11"
msgid "Idaṃ catutthaṃ chakkaṃ. (4)"
msgstr "This is the fourth set of six."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya8"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.282"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "mn148:8.1"
msgid "‘Cha vedanākāyā veditabbā’ti—"
msgstr "‘The six classes of feeling should be understood.’"

msgctxt "mn148:8.2"
msgid "iti kho panetaṃ vuttaṃ. Kiñcetaṃ paṭicca vuttaṃ?"
msgstr "That’s what I said, but why did I say it?"

msgctxt "mn148:8.3"
msgid ""
"Cakkhuñca paṭicca rūpe ca uppajjati cakkhuviññāṇaṃ, tiṇṇaṃ saṅgati phasso, "
"phassapaccayā vedanā;"
msgstr ""
