msgstr "This is the sixth set of six."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya10"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "mn148:10.1"
msgid "‘Cakkhu attā’ti yo vadeyya taṃ na upapajjati."
msgstr "If anyone says, ‘the eye is self,’ that is not tenable."

msgctxt "mn148:10.2"
msgid "Cakkhussa uppādopi vayopi paññāyati."
msgstr "The arising and vanishing of the eye is evident,"

msgctxt "mn148:10.3"
msgid ""
"Yassa kho pana uppādopi vayopi paññāyati, ‘attā me uppajjati ca veti cā’ti "
"iccassa evamāgataṃ hoti."
msgstr "so it would follow that one’s self arises and vanishes."

msgctxt "mn148:10.4"
msgid "Tasmā taṃ na upapajjati:"
msgstr "That’s why it’s not tenable to claim that"

msgctxt "mn148:10.5"
msgid "‘cakkhu attā’ti yo vadeyya."
msgstr "the eye is self."

msgctxt "mn148:10.6"
msgid "Iti cakkhu anattā."
msgstr "So the eye is not self."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "mn148:10.7"
msgid "‘Rūpā attā’ti yo vadeyya taṃ na upapajjati."
msgstr "If anyone says, ‘sights are self,’ that is not tenable."

msgctxt "mn148:10.8"
msgid "Rūpānaṃ uppādopi vayopi paññāyati."
msgstr "The arising and vanishing of sights is evident,"

msgctxt "mn148:10.9"
msgid ""
"Yassa kho pana uppādopi vayopi paññāyati, ‘attā me uppajjati ca veti cā’ti "
"iccassa evamāgataṃ hoti."
msgstr "so it would follow that one’s self arises and vanishes."

msgctxt "mn148:10.10"
msgid "Tasmā taṃ na upapajjati:"
msgstr "That’s why it’s not tenable to claim that"

msgctxt "mn148:10.11"
msgid "‘rūpā attā’ti yo vadeyya."
msgstr "sights are self."

msgctxt "mn148:10.12"
msgid "Iti cakkhu anattā, rūpā anattā."
msgstr "So the eye is not self and sights are not self."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "mn148:10.13"
msgid "‘Cakkhuviññāṇaṃ attā’ti yo vadeyya taṃ na upapajjati."
msgstr "If anyone says, ‘eye consciousness is self,’ that is not tenable."

msgctxt "mn148:10.14"
msgid "Cakkhuviññāṇassa uppādopi vayopi paññāyati."
msgstr "The arising and vanishing of eye consciousness is evident,"

msgctxt "mn148:10.15"
msgid ""
"Yassa kho pana uppādopi vayopi paññāyati, ‘attā me uppajjati ca veti cā’ti "
"iccassa evamāgataṃ hoti."
msgstr "so it would follow that one’s self arises and vanishes."

msgctxt "mn148:10.16"
msgid "Tasmā taṃ na upapajjati:"
msgstr "That’s why it’s not tenable to claim that"

msgctxt "mn148:10.17"
msgid "‘cakkhuviññāṇaṃ attā’ti yo vadeyya."
msgstr "eye consciousness is self."

msgctxt "mn148:10.18"
msgid "Iti cakkhu anattā, rūpā anattā, cakkhuviññāṇaṃ anattā."
msgstr "So the eye, sights, and eye consciousness are not self."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn148:10.19"
msgid "‘Cakkhusamphasso attā’ti yo vadeyya taṃ na upapajjati."
msgstr "If anyone says, ‘eye contact is self,’ that is not tenable."

msgctxt "mn148:10.20"
msgid "Cakkhusamphassassa uppādopi vayopi paññāyati."
msgstr "The arising and vanishing of eye contact is evident,"

msgctxt "mn148:10.21"
msgid ""
"Yassa kho pana uppādopi vayopi paññāyati, ‘attā me uppajjati ca veti cā’ti "
"iccassa evamāgataṃ hoti."
msgstr "so it would follow that one’s self arises and vanishes."

msgctxt "mn148:10.22"
msgid "Tasmā taṃ na upapajjati:"
msgstr "That’s why it’s not tenable to claim that"

msgctxt "mn148:10.23"
msgid "‘cakkhusamphasso attā’ti yo vadeyya."
msgstr "eye contact is self."

msgctxt "mn148:10.24"
msgid ""
"Iti cakkhu anattā, rūpā anattā, cakkhuviññāṇaṃ anattā, cakkhusamphasso "
"anattā."
msgstr "So the eye, sights, eye consciousness, and eye contact are not self."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.283"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "mn148:10.25"
msgid "‘Vedanā attā’ti yo vadeyya taṃ na upapajjati."
msgstr "If anyone says, ‘feeling is self,’ that is not tenable."

msgctxt "mn148:10.26"
msgid "Vedanāya uppādopi vayopi paññāyati."
msgstr "The arising and vanishing of feeling is evident,"

msgctxt "mn148:10.27"
msgid ""
"Yassa kho pana uppādopi vayopi paññāyati, ‘attā me uppajjati ca veti cā’ti "
"iccassa evamāgataṃ hoti."
msgstr "so it would follow that one’s self arises and vanishes."

msgctxt "mn148:10.28"
msgid "Tasmā taṃ na upapajjati:"
msgstr "That’s why it’s not tenable to claim that"

msgctxt "mn148:10.29"
msgid "‘vedanā attā’ti yo vadeyya."
msgstr "feeling is self."

msgctxt "mn148:10.30"
msgid ""
"Iti cakkhu anattā, rūpā anattā, cakkhuviññāṇaṃ anattā, cakkhusamphasso "
"anattā, vedanā anattā."
msgstr ""
"So the eye, sights, eye consciousness, eye contact, and feeling are not self."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "mn148:10.31"
msgid "‘Taṇhā attā’ti yo vadeyya taṃ na upapajjati."
msgstr "If anyone says, ‘craving is self,’ that is not tenable."

msgctxt "mn148:10.32"
msgid "Taṇhāya uppādopi vayopi paññāyati."
msgstr "The arising and vanishing of craving is evident,"

msgctxt "mn148:10.33"
msgid ""
"Yassa kho pana uppādopi vayopi paññāyati, ‘attā me uppajjati ca veti cā’ti "
"iccassa evamāgataṃ hoti."
msgstr "so it would follow that one’s self arises and vanishes."

msgctxt "mn148:10.34"
msgid "Tasmā taṃ na upapajjati:"
msgstr "That’s why it’s not tenable to claim that"

msgctxt "mn148:10.35"
msgid "‘taṇhā attā’ti yo vadeyya."
msgstr "craving is self."

msgctxt "mn148:10.36"
msgid ""
"Iti cakkhu anattā, rūpā anattā, cakkhuviññāṇaṃ anattā, cakkhusamphasso "
"anattā, vedanā anattā, taṇhā anattā."
msgstr ""
"So the eye, sights, eye consciousness, eye contact, feeling, and craving are "
"not self."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "mn148:11.1"
msgid "‘Sotaṃ attā’ti yo vadeyya … pe …"
msgstr "If anyone says, ‘the ear is self’ …"

msgctxt "mn148:11.2"
msgid "‘ghānaṃ attā’ti yo vadeyya … pe …"
msgstr "‘the nose is self’ …"

msgctxt "mn148:11.3"
msgid "‘jivhā attā’ti yo vadeyya … pe …"
msgstr "‘the tongue is self’ …"

msgctxt "mn148:11.4"
msgid "‘kāyo attā’ti yo vadeyya … pe …"
msgstr "‘the body is self’ …"

msgctxt "mn148:11.5"
msgid "‘mano attā’ti yo vadeyya taṃ na upapajjati."
msgstr "‘the mind is self,’ that is not tenable."

msgctxt "mn148:11.6"
msgid "Manassa uppādopi vayopi paññāyati."
msgstr "The arising and vanishing of the mind is evident,"

msgctxt "mn148:11.7"
msgid ""
"Yassa kho pana uppādopi vayopi paññāyati, ‘attā me uppajjati ca veti cā’ti "
"iccassa evamāgataṃ hoti."
msgstr "so it would follow that one’s self arises and vanishes."

msgctxt "mn148:11.8"
msgid "Tasmā taṃ na upapajjati:"
msgstr "That’s why it’s not tenable to claim that"

msgctxt "mn148:11.9"
msgid "‘mano attā’ti yo vadeyya."
msgstr "the mind is self."

msgctxt "mn148:11.10"
msgid "Iti mano anattā."
msgstr "So the mind is not self."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "mn148:12.1"
msgid "‘Dhammā attā’ti yo vadeyya taṃ na upapajjati."
msgstr "If anyone says, ‘thoughts are self’ …"

msgctxt "mn148:12.2"
msgid "Dhammānaṃ uppādopi vayopi paññāyati."
msgstr ""

